'''1919年红色夏季'''（{{lang-en|Red Summer}}）指美国1919年夏季直至初秋發生的一系列血腥[[种族骚乱|种族骚乱]]。

骚乱以白人袭击非裔美国人为主，在多达34个城市发生。某些城市的黑人则相应地做出了反击，引发团体冲突，导致了大量死亡，例如[[1919年芝加哥种族暴动|芝加哥]]、[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]以及阿肯萨斯州的伊莲市（Elaine）<ref name=nyt>''New York Times'': [http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9C04E7D61F30E033A25756C0A9669D946896D6CF "For Action on Race Riot Peril," October 5, 1919] {{Wayback|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9C04E7D61F30E033A25756C0A9669D946896D6CF |date=20160303204459 }}, accessed January 20, 2010. This newspaper article includes several paragraphs of editorial analysis followed by Dr. George E. Haynes' report, "summarized at several points."</ref>。

